T integrates so many services that covering all of them would easily be ten posts on its own. So I just covered a few here. The setup is generally not complicated — most of it is just pasting in an ID. See you in the next one ",[475,476],"d",{},[478,479,480],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":110,"searchDepth":128,"depth":128,"links":482},[483,484,485,486,487],{"id":14,"depth":128,"text":15},{"id":22,"depth":128,"text":23},{"id":89,"depth":128,"text":90},{"id":279,"depth":128,"text":280},{"id":372,"depth":128,"text":373},"Hexo","2020-10-02 00:00:01","md","en",{},true,"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002Flearn-hexo-19-next-third-party","3",{"title":6,"description":19},false,"en\u002FHexo\u002Flearn-hexo-19-next-third-party",[488,500,501,502],"Learning Hexo from Scratch","iThome Ironman 2020","NexT",null,"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F02\u002Flearn-hexo-19-next-third-party\u002F","uy8taGtDaCykSxx7UHNHPQT_MjMckbSir0hFa4Irth4",{"newer":507,"older":511},{"url":508,"title":509,"date":510},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F03\u002Flearn-hexo-20-next-plugins\u002F","(20) Learning Hexo from Scratch - NexT Theme: Plugins You Can Install","2020-10-03 00:00:0